<h4>Features</h4>
<div>
	<p>
		The AWS Driver driver allows you to provision Docker Swarm clusters using <b>AWS Cloud Formation</b> Engine and virtual machine clusters using <b>Terraform</b>.
	</p>
	<p>
		The driver connects to these clusters empowering you to manage and operate in a signle pane of glass.
	</p>
	<p>
		The driver also extends the default functionality that Cloud Formation, Terraform and Docker Swarm offer by adding many features such as:
	</p>
</div>
