				<ul>
					<li>Container Clustering over multi region</li>
					<li>Virtual Machine Clustering over multi region</li>
					<li>Supports Infra Code Templates with Cloud Formation driver</li>
					<li>Supports Infra Code Templates with terraform driver</li>
					<li>Templated environment support</li>
				</ul>
